    <div class="demise">
        <h2>DEMISE</h2>
        <p>He formed the "What Can I Give Movement" to foster a compassionate society. 
On July 27, 2015, he collapsed while delivering a lecture at IIM Shillong and passed away from cardiac arrest at the age of 83. </p>
